/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T23:21:29.000Z","msg":"知唔知點解你唔識反駁<br />\n<br />\n因為佢根本就唔係答緊條問題<br />\n<br />\n人地問點解移民，佢就答「移民係我嘅自由」，但姐係點解要移？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4abdf48650a15c951f4170ad1451fd971cdff3a","tid":2140062,"uid":190639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T23:27:27.000Z","msg":"係愛國嘅點解唔貢獻自己嘅力量知識報效祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n振興中華<br />\n而係輸出去俾人地國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本出得國<br />\n愛國只係象徵式，掛喺口邊一句口號<br />\n等自己個心好過啲"},{"pid":"5a03ec11333f369650f6008c143ede90d7768450","tid":2140062,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4da320faab737ff15e069305ca83bb043943cb90","tid":2140062,"uid":38904,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T17:16:55.000Z","msg":"移民是生活<br />\n愛国是工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T23:33:22.000Z","msg":"反美是工作 生活在美國"},{"pid":"b3f1632420cde5526499603fc3d1b2a3925ad212","tid":2140062,"uid":130466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"92a31c4aa8a521d31463b41f0bdfdb4336aa38b8","tid":2140062,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T17:13:48.000Z","msg":"我諗咗好耐都諗唔到 <br />\n<br />\n移民外國嘅小粉紅如果俾人問既然咁愛中國 點解仲要移民？<br />\n<br />\n雖然你知 我知 佢知 單眼佬都知個真正原因就係本身住個度唔好<br />\n<br />\n心裡面就咁諗啫 但無理由講偉大祖國唔好吖<br />\n<br />\n究竟佢地有咩藉口話俾人聽點解要移民呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T23:36:39.000Z","msg":"佢地打橫黎講。會覺得佢地肯黎係人地汁到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咪諗住同佢地講親理，班人好撚賤係要人用支共果套同佢鬥拳頭大"},{"pid"